%% MLflow Tracking Server - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/mlflow.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Client / SDK
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant AuthPlugin as Kubernetes Auth<br/>Middleware
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WP as Workspace Provider
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: ML Experiment Logging

    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/3.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-Mlflow-Workspace
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: Authorize request
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>resource: experiments<br/>group: mlflow.kubeflow.org
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed/Denied
    AuthPlugin-->>MLflow: Authorization result

    MLflow->>WP: Resolve workspace
    WP->>K8sAPI: Check namespace cache<br/>Watch MLflowConfig
    K8sAPI-->>WP: Namespace + Config

    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run metadata<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID

    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/3.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT metric data

    Client->>MLflow: PUT /api/3.0/mlflow/artifacts<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MLflow->>S3: Upload artifact<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload confirmed

    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Workspace Resolution

    Client->>MLflow: GET /api/3.0/mlflow/experiments/list<br/>Header: X-Mlflow-Workspace: my-namespace
    MLflow->>WP: Resolve workspace "my-namespace"
    WP->>K8sAPI: Lookup namespace in cache
    WP->>K8sAPI: Lookup MLflowConfig (optional)
    K8sAPI-->>WP: MLflowConfig with artifactRootSecret
    WP->>K8sAPI: GET Secret mlflow-artifact-connection<br/>in namespace my-namespace
    K8sAPI-->>WP: S3 bucket config
    WP-->>MLflow: Workspace context with artifact root
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments<br/>WHERE workspace = 'my-namespace'
    PG-->>MLflow: Experiment list
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK (experiments)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    Client->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>Content-Type: application/x-protobuf<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>AuthPlugin: Authorize (experiments scope)
    AuthPlugin->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>AuthPlugin: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans
    PG-->>MLflow: Stored
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK
